Egy Metro Guide takes your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy describes how the app collects, uses, and protects your information.

**IMPORTANT DISCLAIMER**
Egy Metro Guide is an independent application and is NOT owned by, affiliated with, endorsed by, or representing the Egyptian government or any governmental entity. All metro information is sourced from publicly available government resources.

**Information Collection and Use**
Egy Metro Guide does not collect, store, or share any personal or sensitive user data. The app does not use a backend server and does not require users to sign in or provide personal information.

The app may access your device's location only when it is actively in use, in order to:
- Help you find the nearest metro station
- Provide relevant station and transportation information

Location access is optional and used solely on the user's device. No location data is sent to external servers or stored in any way.

**Subscription Services**
Egy Metro Guide offers optional subscription services to provide enhanced features and an ad-free experience. Subscription payments are processed through Google Play Store's billing system. We do not collect or store payment information directly - all payment processing is handled securely by Google Play Store.

**Advertising**
Egy Metro Guide uses Google AdMob to display ads (including banner, interstitial, and open app ads). AdMob may collect limited data (such as device identifiers and usage statistics) to personalize and improve ad relevance.

For more information on how Google uses data from AdMob, please visit:
https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads

**Cookies**
While this app does not use cookies directly, AdMob may use cookies and similar technologies for ad personalization and analytics.

**Third-Party Links**
The app may include links to external websites or official government sources. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third-party sites.

**Data Security**
Since Egy Metro Guide does not collect or store personal data, there are no concerns regarding personal data storage or transmission. Users are encouraged to use the app from secure and trusted devices.

**Changes to This Privacy Policy**
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page.

